    <summary>Git-based version control system optimized for large media files</summary>
    <description>
MediaGit is a modern version control system designed specifically for managing large binary files such as images, videos, 3D models, and machine learning datasets. It provides:

* Fast branch switching (under 100ms)
* Intelligent compression and deduplication
* Media-aware merge capabilities
* Support for multiple cloud storage backends (S3, Azure, GCS, MinIO)
* Git-compatible workflow

Perfect for game development, VFX, machine learning, and any project dealing with large binary assets.
    </description>
